# WARNING: Do _NOT_ use whitespaces (` ') or tab (`	')
# characters in any of the variables below save for MAKEFLAGS,
# PATH, and TIMESTAMP_FMT.
#
# $PREFIX_{NATIVE,TARGET} and $WORKDIR must be immediately
